We use disk images in DF because it makes it easier to manage any evidence that we receive.

To prevent a USB from going beack and forth across the US, we can just make a disk image of the USB and be able to have 
its info so we can send it anywhere and not have and complications

The steps to create a empty disk image is to:
fallocate
cfdisk
kpartx
mkfs


The OSI model related to the disk image because every OSI has its own unique disk image 
